Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95408,97493}Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97493,99329}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99579,102290}She's heading for the\Nexit on the first floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103124,106044}Just as I suspected.\NI know she'll come out this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:50.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109964,110882}Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112467,114177}I've got you now, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:57.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116971,117889}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:01:59.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118348,119432}Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121809,123019}Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123019,124062}Better luck next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:07.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125938,127273}Be seeing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:11.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127732,131235}She's getting away again! Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.95,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:135948,137950}{\an2}Dolphins Vs. Eagles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139535,141579}St. Tail dropped these?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:28.16,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:144624,148169}Pinch! Beware of Lost Objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164894,167063}My form's not all that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174779,176489}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176489,178032}I shouldn't have\Ndone that in the chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178282,179200}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179659,180785}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:07.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182954,187333}Oh! Are you Oikawa, the pitcher\Nfor the Southern Rainbow Dolphins?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:08.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187333,188876}You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:12.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189252,192004}Of course, you're a celebrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:18.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193297,198219}I was until last month.\NI'm on a losing streak now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:21.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198219,201347}Don't give up.\NMy prayers are with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202432,204016}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204016,207061}And what brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208020,209439}Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:34.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210773,214569}I may not be of much help,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:37.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214569,217155}but you can share\Nyour troubles with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:48.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221492,228332}The truth is I lost my lucky glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228332,229333}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234797,237383}Strike three! You're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:05.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238885,245266}The daughter of our owner's\Nfriend wanted my autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249187,250688}May I have your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252523,253483}Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:18.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254567,258446}I asked her to hold the glove\Nwhile I signed her board.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261324,262658}But then…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:28.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264827,268873}Both she and my glove disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:34.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270041,274045}This was the glove I had used\Nwhen I pitched a no-hitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274045,277715}It brought me luck, and\NI'd been using it ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277715,279008}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:44.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279008,284096}Our next game\Nis for the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:48.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284096,288559}I came here to pray\Nfor her to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289018,291896}When is the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:55.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291896,295566}This Sunday, against the Eagles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:03.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298110,303741}Have faith, the Lord\Nis looking out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:11.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306744,311958}…and that's why I want you\Nto get his glove back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312458,314335}Okay, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314335,315962}The truth is…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317713,319757}…ta-daa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320299,323261}I've got tickets to Sunday's game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326180,327473}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327473,328474}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329684,330810}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:34.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331394,334814}I lost the tickets to\Nthe Dolphins game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334814,338276}I didn't know you\Nwere a baseball fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:43.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340152,343614}No, it's not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:48.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343614,348327}Remember math class\Nthe other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349328,351330}Your score is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:59.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354584,359046}If you score below 30 again I'll revoke\Nyour recess and you'll have to go to study hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359046,360006}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361215,362592}Tough luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362592,363718}Mister Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363718,364343}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:07.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364844,367096}I want you to tutor Miss Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367096,368055}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:11.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368639,371517}Having an honor student\Ntutor her should help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371976,374228}– Oh, no! Not him!\N– Oh, no! Not her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:20.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375146,380693}Enough of that! This is not\Na request, it's an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:25.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381235,385531}I don't quite remember the incident,\Nbut how lucky for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:30.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385531,390661}That's not luck! Do you know\Nwhat he did after class?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:37.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391704,397084}You know, I'd really like to see the\Nnext Dolphins game at the Big Dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:43.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398794,403049}Let's make a deal, Miss Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403049,405676}Are you telling me to treat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:49.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406093,409680}Or you can stay in\Nstudy hall during recess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:50.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409680,410222}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:53.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410222,413100}No, no! It'll be my\Npleasure to treat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:58.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414810,418439}The creep had me cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418439,420066}So you have a date with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421275,423903}You must be looking\Nforward to Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424362,426322}Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426322,428199}It was blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:11.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428199,431994}I had to beg Papa for the tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:17.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433871,437375}And after all that, I've lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439585,441754}What should I do, Seira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442463,446133}Well, anyway, let's go\Nlook for them tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449053,451263}Tickets to the Dolphins game?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451764,454558}I must have dropped them.\NHave you seen them around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454558,455768}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455768,457228}Neither have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457228,458521}Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458521,460648}The Dolphins are so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460648,463442}I doubt you'll get more tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:47.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463442,467029}Shh! Don't talk so loud.\NHe might hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467029,468197}Hey, Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:53.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468948,473661}Don't forget about Sunday and\NI promise you'll score 100 on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:08:00.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476998,480876}She promised to take\NAsuka to that game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:01.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480876,481836}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482461,483838}You're going with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483838,486632}You two are always fighting!\NWhat gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486882,490219}It's not like that!\NI can explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491012,492471}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:16.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492471,496308}Um, anyway, I lost the tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:23.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499478,503274}{\i1}The tickets St. Tail dropped,\Nand the tickets Haneoka lost…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:27.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504066,507236}{\i1}…are for the same Dolphins game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507236,508654}{\i1}Could she be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:43.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519832,523335}{\i1}Now I remember! I had them\Nwith me on that last caper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:52.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528507,532803}{\i1}That's it, I must have lost them\Nwhile I was escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541771,543647}Good show, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543647,545691}That was a 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545816,549153}No, I just got lucky, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550488,552323}{\i1}I think I overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:17.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552907,557620}{\i1}Such technique…\NQuite extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558245,559413}{\i1}It must be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559413,560623}There it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560623,562249}Fall back! Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:23.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562249,563584}Get it, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:34.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571717,574178}Who picked him to be goal keeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574178,576764}Asuka, are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578599,579892}Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:46.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580684,586857}"Tonight, I will enter the Uehara residence\Nfor pitcher Oikawa's glove. Signed, St. Tail".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587942,591153}Hey, Asuka, it's a\Nchallenge from St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592154,593614}Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594240,595616}Snap out of it, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596075,598828}I just don't get it,\Nboth St. Tail and Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598828,601038}Why are they always after this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601622,603833}Pay attention, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:07.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603833,607294}Meimi Haneoka…\Nyou're mighty suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609130,611632}Now, to go look for those tickets…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613217,615177}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615177,617596}I… I have to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:22.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618264,622434}No way!\NThe test is tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:40.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635364,640619}Solving trigonometry problems\Nis like a criminal investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:45.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640619,645166}You find each and every clue,\Nfit them into place, until…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645166,647168}Bam! See, you've\Nsolved the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647168,649837}Is detective work all\Nyou ever think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649837,652464}Mathematics is one of the\Nfoundations of detective work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654049,656844}Is arresting St. Tail\Nthat important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662224,663767}Well, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664518,665644}None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:07.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666854,667897}What's that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668439,670566}It's between St. Tail and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671483,673652}Why can't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679533,681160}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:25.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681160,685331}Now, the next problem.\NIf you take one figure on a flat plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:31.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685331,691795}and move each of its points\Nin the same direction by a fixed distance…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691795,693172}Hey. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693172,695382}Miss Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696133,698093}I'd like to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704892,707811}What is it, Miss Takamiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:52.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711523,712483}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713901,716320}Aren't these yours?
Comment: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:02.74,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:722743,722743}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:08.74,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:728749,728749}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:13.50,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:733504,733504}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:18.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734588,738467}Actually I found these\Nthe other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739885,742429}Do you want to know\Nwhere I found them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:33.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747893,753148}Um, thanks, but these aren't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754358,756110}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:39.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756110,759113}Well then, I guess\NI'll keep them for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762992,766620}Asuka is a big Dolphins fan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:51.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767329,771583}I'm sure he'll be happy to go,\Nif I ask him. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773752,775629}Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775838,777131}What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:00.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777131,780676}The game's this Sunday\Nand I don't have the tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782052,785306}And of all people,\Nwhy'd Rina have to find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787474,790227}I've got to get those tickets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790227,793605}But I could get caught. Still…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796442,797484}Still…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798360,799653}Don't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:25.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801071,805951}He was so excited about going.\NI can't just tell him it's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:33.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808620,813417}I said no! This is mine and\NI'm not letting anyone take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:37.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813792,817671}But you have to put\Nthe glove on that table.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:38.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817671,818714}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:41.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818714,821884}What's so important\Nabout this table?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822051,823594}Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828307,830684}What is this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:56.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830684,836690}A special fluorescent paint.\NI'm using it to expose St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837232,840611}Why are you so obsessed\Nwith St. Tail, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:04.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841070,844114}I told you, I'm going to\Nbecome a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844114,846742}I'm not letting that ridiculous\Npetty thief get the best of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848118,849870}A ridiculous petty thief, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:12.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850537,852539}Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852539,853374}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:19.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854583,859546}I've got a great idea.\NThis time, we do a double-cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:24.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860881,864593}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:32.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870849,872059}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874353,875729}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877689,879525}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894248,897918}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899253,902256}Be careful, remember\Nyour last caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902256,903006}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913475,915352}We've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915644,917354}The real glove is at the Big Dome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:18.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917646,918355}Grab her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:20.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919857,920941}Did we get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920941,922276}Sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922276,923318}Turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924653,927156}What?!?\NIt's a dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:34.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930617,934204}Damn! She got past us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934913,936331}So, it was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:44.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938917,944173}Oikawa's glove, huh?\NBoy, you're lucky that I'm a big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944173,946717}Too bad, you can't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949178,950929}Asuka…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:55.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951388,955642}I have tickets to the Dolphins game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:57.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956685,957853}{\i1}Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958896,960856}Will… will you go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:08.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964526,968071}Sorry, but I'm already\Ngoing with Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:18.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971909,978040}Oh, really? I just hope she\Nremembers her promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:18.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978040,978749}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:23.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979833,983545}I know who St. Tail is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985964,987674}Shall I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988342,989176}{\i1}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000687,1001688}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004274,1005567}Don't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006360,1008278}I just want to capture her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:59.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016537,1019915}{\i1}I don't care who she is. I just\Nwant to capture her on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:06.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025379,1026713}A breeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028507,1030259}The dome roof is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041436,1042563}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043188,1044106}Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045232,1047109}How'd you know we were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047109,1049570}Never mind that, quickly, arrest her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:31.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049570,1051613}And here's the first pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051613,1054491}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054783,1055784}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056034,1058620}And we're already in the 7th inning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068964,1071300}Asuka, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072175,1073552}It's out of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074761,1076722}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076722,1078849}Oh, be quiet! Stop your bawling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079224,1082227}All right, let's end\Nthe game, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083353,1084021}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:04.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084021,1084730}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:05.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084730,1085397}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:22.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098869,1102122}I'm giving this back\Nto pitcher Oikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102122,1105375}You may be his fan,\Nbut taking his glove was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105834,1106668}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:29.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106668,1109880}She stole the glove?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:32.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109880,1112299}I'll never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:37.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112758,1117763}And I'll take these back, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118430,1119931}Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120265,1121933}St. Tail! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:56.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135614,1136615}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142496,1145248}{\i1}Thank you, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152255,1154800}Man! How many times\Ndo I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:18.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154800,1158553}Listen, meet me at gate #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:21.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158553,1161807}You listen! I don't know\Nwhere gate #2 is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161807,1164559}I told you, it's the\Nentrance on the North end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:27.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164559,1167145}And which side is North?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167145,1168980}You're so helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:34.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168980,1174361}{\i1}Meimi Haneoka,\NI'll get you next time.
