Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:45.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181618,1185372}On the mound is Oikawa, who hasn't\Nbeen doing too well the past few games.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:48.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185372,1188625}Let's see what he has\Nin store for us today.
