Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198427,1200470}Strike! You're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201304,1202848}What a fastball!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:06.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202848,1206393}Three strikes! Looks like\NOikawa is out of his slump.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206393,1208103}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:14.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211148,1214067}Oikawa has struck out\Nthree batters in this inning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:18.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215569,1218488}He's really looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218488,1219406}Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:33.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229708,1233253}{\i1}No! I just want to\Ncapture her on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236381,1238049}I guess we have to thank St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:43.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240385,1243805}Why are you blushing? Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:48.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244222,1248268}You wouldn't understand.\NIt's very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249060,1250437}{\i1}I love you!
